extract intensities and annotations from MQ proteinGroups.txt

Source: R/tidyMS_MQProteinGroups.R
tidyMQ_ProteinGroups.Rd

extract intensities and annotations from MQ proteinGroups.txt

tidyMQ_ProteinGroups(MQProteinGroups)

Arguments

MQProteinGroups

data.frame generated with read.csv("peptide.txt",sep="\t", stringsAsFactors=FALSE)

See also

Other MaxQuant: plot_MQ_intensity_vs_retention_time(), tidyMQ_Evidence(), tidyMQ_PeptideProtein(), tidyMQ_Peptides_Config(), tidyMQ_Peptides(), tidyMQ_allPeptides(), tidyMQ_from_Sites(), tidyMQ_from_modSpecific_to_peptide(), tidyMQ_merged(), tidyMQ_modificationSpecificPeptides(), tidyMQ_top_protein_name()

Examples

protein_txt <- system.file("samples/maxquant_txt/MSQC1/proteinGroups.txt",package = "LFQService")
protein_txt <- read.csv(protein_txt, header=TRUE, stringsAsFactors = FALSE, sep="\t")
mq_proteins <-tidyMQ_ProteinGroups(protein_txt)
head(mq_proteins)
